//                                  WITHOUT delegating to any `HostCap`.
//   CELL 5 (user-extended cap)     `repl_runtime.cell_5(..., 42)` — the
//                                  call reaches a `HostCap` registered
//                                  via `HostCaps::register` (any cap
//                                  written outside the built-in registry).
